Definition: containing or expressing accusation
Example: an accusative forefinger; black accusatory looks; accusive shoes and telltale trousers- O.Henry; his accusing glare
Synonyms: noun, communication, verb, accuse, accusatory, accusing, accusive, containing, or, expressing, accusation, an, forefinger, black, looks, shoes, and, telltale, trousers, -, O, Henry, his, glare
Category: adj.all
